metadata.name: From the Dust
metadata.description:
“From the Dust” | Day 6 Pt 1 | Creation Series

The making of Adam and Eve in the Garden.

"So the Lord God caused the man to fall into a deep sleep; and while he was sleeping, he took one of the man’s ribs and then closed up the place with flesh. Then the Lord God made a woman from the rib he had taken out of the man, and he brought her to the man to behold." - Gen 2

First owner of this NFT will receive a 20x20 painted framed canvas of this piece signed by the artist.
